<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="799" height="480" viewBox="0 0 799 480"><rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="white"/><rect x="24" y="24" width="120" height="32" rx="4" ry="4" fill="#f6f6f6" stroke="#111" stroke-width="1"/><text x="84" y="45" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace" font-size="13" fill="#111111">A</text><rect x="184" y="24" width="120" height="32" rx="4" ry="4" fill="#f6f6f6" stroke="#111" stroke-width="1"/><text x="244" y="45" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace" font-size="13" fill="#111111">B</text><line x1="84" y1="56" x2="84" y2="424" stroke="#555" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="6 4"/><line x1="244" y1="56" x2="244" y2="424" stroke="#555" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="6 4"/><rect x="24" y="200" width="730" height="56" rx="2" ry="2" fill="#eef6ff" stroke="#666" stroke-width="1"/><polygon points="24,200 56,200 56,214 50,220 24,220" fill="#eef6ff" stroke="#666" stroke-width="1"/><text x="30" y="214" font-family="monospace" font-size="11" font-weight="600" fill="#111">ref</text><text x="32" y="232" font-family="monospace" font-size="12" fill="#111">External dependency handshake with a very long descriptive line that previously escaped the ref block.</text><text x="32" y="248" font-family="monospace" font-size="12" fill="#111">Return payload includes another long descriptive line to stress multiline measurement.</text><rect x="24" y="280" width="751" height="120" rx="2" ry="2" fill="#fafafa" stroke="#666" stroke-width="1"/><polygon points="24,280 771,280 771,294 765,300 24,300" fill="#fafafa" stroke="#666" stroke-width="1"/><text x="32" y="294" font-family="monospace" font-size="12" font-weight="600" fill="#111">group This group label is intentionally verbose so the container width follows measured content correctly</text><line x1="84" y1="88" x2="244" y2="88" stroke="#111" stroke-width="1.5"/><polygon points="244,88 236,83 236,93" fill="#111" stroke="#111" stroke-width="1"/><text x="92" y="80" text-anchor="start" font-family="monospace" font-size="12" fill="#111">kickoff</text><line x1="84" y1="328" x2="244" y2="328" stroke="#111" stroke-width="1.5"/><polygon points="244,328 236,323 236,333" fill="#111" stroke="#111" stroke-width="1"/><text x="92" y="320" text-anchor="start" font-family="monospace" font-size="12" fill="#111">work</text><path d="M24,120 H713 L727 134 V168 H24 Z" fill="#fff8c4" stroke="#111" stroke-width="1"/><path d="M713 120 V134 H727" fill="none" stroke="#111" stroke-width="1"/><text x="32" y="140" font-family="monospace" font-size="12" fill="#111">This is a very long yellow note line that should force the container to grow wider than defaults.</text><text x="32" y="156" font-family="monospace" font-size="12" fill="#111">And this second line keeps the multiline height constraints honest.</text><rect x="24" y="424" width="120" height="32" rx="4" ry="4" fill="#f6f6f6" stroke="#111" stroke-width="1"/><text x="84" y="445" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace" font-size="13" fill="#111111">A</text><rect x="184" y="424" width="120" height="32" rx="4" ry="4" fill="#f6f6f6" stroke="#111" stroke-width="1"/><text x="244" y="445" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace" font-size="13" fill="#111111">B</text></svg>
